# Data & outputs — never commit market data or run artifacts.
# Anchored with a leading slash so ONLY the repo-root data/ (and runs/) folders are
# ignored — an unanchored "data/" also matched the aegis_brain/data/ SOURCE package
# and silently kept the CRSP/WRDS loaders out of version control. *.parquet/*.db
# below are the real belt-and-suspenders guard against any stray data file anywhere.
/data/
/runs/
*.csv.gz
*.parquet
*.db
*.xlsx

